1.0.name: wordpress/web2carz
1.0.description:
The plug-in will allow a user to search for a vehicle of their choice (Make & Model) in their area (Zip Code + Radius). The search results will bring back the basic information (photo, year, price, mileage) on the vehicles as well as point the user to the main vehicle detail page on Web2Carz.com. The widget is AJAX enabled so results will return without leaving the current page. A revenue share is available to the blog owner for referral traffic conversions.

  • To obtain a revenue share relationship, please contact Web2Carz directly for a custom affiliateId. Contact email: affiliate[at]web2carz.com.
